NUMBER 3371
NAME Subterranean Garden
REGION 206
DEEPCAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 76
CALL 19
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Mysterious plants of all shapes and sizes grow in lush abundance, each one
carefully shaped and tended by the silent caretakers that move amongst
them like benevolent wraiths. A deep stream winds through the garden,
sometimes crossing the sandy path that leads through this place.
Miniscule creatures that glow soft blue, green, and violet dart about
in the clear water. Each one emits barely enough light to illuminate
itself, but together they create an ever-changing tapestry of cool
radiance beneath the stream's surface.
*DESCRIPTION_END
