; icy cold clear water (in the fountain)
ITEM 9 693
; ucantsee
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The passage itself is unlit, but the dim glow of magelight from either end
provides sufficient illumination.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The symbols are not engraved or set into the stone by any traditional
crafter's means, but rather seem to glimmer just below the surface of the
stone as though part of the substance itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
Fine pale sand, raked smooth of any trace of footprints, glimmers faintly
in the phosphorescent glow of the garden.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
The faint, pleasantly musky smells of old leather and parchment accompany
the soft rustle of pages from the room beyond.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 4
Crystal clear water cascades down from thin air to fall in sparkling
rivulets across the impossibly delicate stone strands of the web.
Diamond-bright drops cling to the outer edges like early morning dew.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO GROUP You walk down the passage, your footsteps echoing on the polished floor.
  ECHO OTHGROUP %P walks down the passage, footsteps echoing on the polished floor.
  MOVEGROUP 3370
  AFFECT 3370
  ECHO OTHERS The guardian statues turn to watch the arrival of %P.
  AFFECT 3371
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO GROUP You make your way along the shadowy path through the underground garden.
  ECHO OTHGROUP %P moves off along the shadowy path through the underground garden.
  MOVEGROUP 3384
  AFFECT 3384
  ECHO OTHERS %P arrives from the garden path.
  AFFECT 3371
ENDIF
