NUMBER 3372
NAME Shrine Antechamber
REGION 206
DEEPCAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 76
CALL 19
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The steep walls of this round chamber climb to meet seamlessly in a domed
ceiling high overhead. A richly detailed, colorful mural covers every inch
of the vertical surface, in intriguing contrast to the neutral gray stone
of the curved roof and the stark black-and-white pattern of the mosaic
that forms the floor. Although no other exits are visible save for the
arch leading back out to the garden, there is a sense of otherworldliness
to the place that causes a slight sense of both anticipation and unease.
*DESCRIPTION_END
