EXTEND 1 of numerous Powers worshiped by the Dark Elves of Andor
ITEM 2 547 ADJ1=348 ADJ2=265
; wide round mosaic
EXTEND 2 of a silver and white spiderweb upon a midnight black background
ITEM 9 693
; ucantsee
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The symbols are not engraved or set into the stone by any traditional
crafter's means, but rather seem to glimmer just below the surface of the
stone as though part of the substance itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
There are no borders or lines separating each Power's illustrations from
the others. Instead, they all blend together into the pantheon that they
are: sometimes allies, sometimes rivals, always together.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
Tiny bits of flat, polished stone have been mortared together to form a
larger image. The pieces are so closely fitted that one has to look very
closely to see any seams between them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
