NUMBER 3373
NAME Shrine of Aggreh
REGION 206
DEEPCAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 76
CALL 19
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Every combination of the elements swirls within the raw force that shapes
the walls of this chamber. Fire and earth, wind and water, light and
shadow all mingle and transform one another as they touch, forming an
ever-changing tapestry of power. Every surface constantly transforms
in slow motion, except for a strange ring of stable substance in the
precise center of the floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=287 ADJ2=647 VAL2=3372
; shimmering crystalline arch
EXTEND 0 traced through with myriad veins of different stone
ITEM 1 334 ADJ1=348 ADJ2=209
; wide mysterious ring
EXTEND 1 seemingly formed of intermingled elemental forces
ITEM 9 693
; ucantsee
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Fragments of every imaginable stone, from flawless diamond to rough
granite, shimmer within an unidentifiable crystal so clear it is
barely visible.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The circumference is divided into six equal arcs, with each one formed
from one of the fundamental elements. Fire dances in its own heat-shimmer,
across from its counterpart Water, and so on for each of the opposing
pairs. In the center is a perfect void, the absence of every element,
just as the chamber outside is the blending of all of them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you step through the arch, the shrine vanishes behind you.
  ECHO OTHERS %N steps through the archway leading back into the antechamber.
  DISBAND
  MOVE 3372
  AFFECT 3372
  ECHO OTHERS %N arrives through a shimmering crystalline arch that vanishes behind %i.
  AFFECT 3373
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TOUCH 1
  IFVAR POSITION = 3
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO ALL %N reaches out and touches the edge of the magical circle.
