*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
Smooth, rounded stones have been carefully placed to line the rim of the
pool. Tiny phosphorescent fish dart among the feathery water plants, bright
flashes of blue and green in the dark water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You stretch out and relax on the bed, leaning back against the luxuruiant pillows.
  ECHO OTHERS %N stretches out and relaxes on the bed, leaning back against the luxuriant pillows.
  POSITION LAY
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Surely the loss of such an obviously favored item would be quickly noticed.
   ECHO OTHERS %N contemplates taking the chimes down, but decides against it.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STEAL 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Surely the loss of such an obviously favored item would be quickly noticed.
   ECHO OTHERS %N contemplates taking the chimes down, but decides against it.
ENDIF
