NUMBER 3389
NAME Guest Room
REGION 206
DEEPCAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 76
CALL 19
CALL 33
SPELL 250
*DESCRIPTION_START
Quiet, melodious jingling emanates from a complex set of chimes hung above
the large comfortable bed, stirred by a gentle magical breeze. The notes
blend with the sound of rippling water from a small stone fountain in the
far corner. Lush indigo moss, dry yet supple, completely covers the floor
from wall to wall, making chairs unnecessary. Tiny luminous gemstones shine
from the ceiling overhead, further enhancing the illusion of being outside
on a clear moonless night.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 946 ADJ1=241 ADJ2=107 VAL2=3387 UNLATCHED
; polished ebony door (to Corridor)
ITEM 1 84 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=63
; large comfortable bed
EXTEND 1 with black sheets woven of the finest spidersilk
ITEM 2 969 ADJ1=90 ADJ2=658 ADJ3=77
; delicate silvery crystal chime
ITEM 3 197 ADJ1=294 ADJ2=25 ADJ3=187
; small black marble fountain
EXTEND 3 formed from a tiny natural spring channeled into a shallow pool
PUT 3 198 ADJ1=67 ADJ2=56 VAL2=100
; cool clear water
PUT 3 380 ADJ1=752 ADJ2=29
; iridescent blue fish
PUT 3 380 ADJ1=752 ADJ2=152
; iridescent green fish
ITEM 9 693
; ucantsee
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Not a scratch mars the precious material. Amazingly, the door seems to be
fashioned from a single enormous piece of wood, leaving one pondering the 
size of the tree it must have been cut from.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
A single occupant could almost get pleasantly lost in this grand, lavish
bed. The frame is solid black marble and hence makes none of the usual
creaks and rustles of a metal or wooden support.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
Long, faceted pieces of a mysterious iridescent crystal have been suspended
with nearly invisible strands of spidersilk from a large silver ring. They 
form an intricate spiraling pattern, sending out beautiful clear tones at
the slightest disturbance in the air around them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
