NUMBER 3390
NAME Infirmary
REGION 206
DEEPCAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 76
CALL 19
HEALER
SPELL 250
*DESCRIPTION_START
Several low cots are arranged around the room for the relative comfort of
the wounded while the healers attend to their injuries. Devotees of
Sarayan and Gazae move confidently about in their gray or colorful robes,
addressing all but the most serious of the hurts, while solemn dark-robed
servants of Lur Masada oversee the treatment of the gravely injured.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=348 ADJ2=150 ADJ3=312 VAL2=3384
; wide gray stone arch (to Training Area)
EXTEND 0 etched with the rune of healing
ITEM 1 436 ADJ1=396 ADJ2=1225
; low sturdy cot
ITEM 9 693
; ucantsee
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The gray stone of the arch shows the wear of constant cleaning... probably
to remove frequent bloodstains.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
A mesh of broad leather strips is tightly woven and tied to a metal frame
to create a light but sturdy and suprisingly comfortable resting place.
*DESCRIPTION_END
TRAINING 20 25
